---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import ownerImage from '../assets/owner.jpg';
import { firm } from '../data/site';
---

<section class="section">
	<div class="shell spotlight-grid">
		<div class="portrait-card">
			<div class="portrait-frame">
				<Image
					src={ownerImage}
					alt="Tracy A. Cinocca"
					widths={[360, 520, 720]}
					sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 34vw"
					loading="lazy"
					format="avif"
				/>
			</div>
			<div class="portrait-caption">
				<strong>Tracy A. Cinocca, J.D.</strong>
				<span>{firm.serviceArea}</span>
				<span>{firm.fullAddress}</span>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="band">
			<p class="eyebrow">Meet Tracy</p>
			<h2 class="section-title">Attorney-led review from a Tulsa office serving clients across Oklahoma.</h2>
			<p class="lead">
				People usually reach out because they need to know whether an injury matter is worth pursuing,
				which planning documents need attention, or what the smartest legal next step looks like before
				time and money are wasted.
			</p>
			<ul class="checklist">
				<li>Tulsa office near Bixby and Broken Arrow</li>
				<li>Attorney-led review instead of a generic intake handoff</li>
				<li>Clear next-step guidance on injury, planning, family, and business matters</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="quote" style="margin-top: 18px;">
				Most people are not looking for a speech. They want to know whether the matter fits, what needs attention first, and what should happen next.
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
